.container-fluid
  .screen-title
    Capital Allocation Decision Entry
  .pull-right
  .jumbotron.screen-instructions

    Allocate your bank's capital across the business units below. The relative profitability of these business units will change as economic and market conditions change. Your goal in this simulation is to maximize your bank's overall profitability. Your total allocation must equal 100%.Please note that you are limited to changing each value by 3% up or down. When complete, click the "Save Decisions" button to save your work before continuing.

